WEBVTT

00:00:04.168 --> 00:00:08.336
Shah Rukh Khan: Why are some people
still unhappy despite having it all in life?

00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:12.296
And some people are happy
despite having very little?

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:16.216
We will get an answer to this
from our next speaker

00:00:16.239 --> 00:00:18.976
who is an expert on happiness.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.896
He has been researching
happiness for years.

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:26.416
He has even developed
a course on the subject,

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:30.696
which is rated among the top 50
online courses in the world.